\v 861 Rerekai nzeve dzenyu, Jehovha, ndipindurei; Nokuti ndiri murombo nomushaiwi.
\p
\v 2 Chengetai mweya wangu; nokuti ndiri mudikanwi wenyu; Haiwa Mwari wangu,
\s ponesai muranda wenyu anovimba nemi.
\p
\v 3 Ndinzwirei ngoni, Ishe;
\s Nokuti ndinodana kwamuri zuva rose.
\p
\v 4 Fadzai mweya womuranda wenyu; Nokuti ndinosimudzira mweya wangu
\s kwamuri Ishe wangu.
\p
\v 5 Nokuti imi, Ishe makanaka, munofarira kukanganwira, Mune ngoni zhinji kuna vose
\s vanodana kwamuri.
\p
\v 6 Rerekerai nzeve yenyu,
\s Jehovha kumunyengetero wangu; Teererai izwi rokukumbira kwangu.
\p
\v 7 Pazuva rokutambudzika kwangu ndichadana kwamuri,
\s Nokuti muchandipindura.
\p
\v 8 Hapana akafanana nemi pakati pavamwari, Ishe,
\s Uye hapana mabasa akafanana namabasa enyu.
\p
\v 9 Ndudzi dzose dzamakaita dzichauya kuzonamata pamberi penyu, Ishe,
\s Dzicharumbidza zita renyu.
